OL,7,FBut he insisted his campaign for
OL,8,Fjustice for himself and his fellow sub-
OL,9,Fpostmasters was "something you
OL,10,Fcouldn't put down" after seeing the
OL,11,F"harm that had been descended upon
OL,12,Fthem".
OL,14,FMr Bates - whose story recently became
OL,15,Fthe subject of ITV drama Mr Bates vs
OL,16,FThe Post Office - also took aim at the
OL,17,Fgovernment's "fundamental flaw" of
OL,18,Fbeing unable to deal with issues such
OL,19,Fas the Horizon scandal "easily and
OL,20,Fsensibly".
