OL,7,FThe campaigner said the mediation
OL,8,Fscheme set up to address the scandal
OL,9,Fwas part of a "cover-up" and a
OL,10,F"fishing expedition" to discover what
OL,11,Fevidence sub-postmasters had about
OL,12,FHorizon.
OL,14,FThe inquiry heard how Mr Bates - who
OL,15,Fsaid he flagged issues with Fujitsu's
OL,16,Ffaulty Horizon system for years - was
OL,17,Feventually sacked because the Post
OL,18,FOffice considered him "unmanageable".
