OL,7,FThough Mr Bates was only a sub-
OL,8,Fpostmaster for five years, he told the
OL,9,Finquiry he has spent 23 years
OL,10,Fcampaigning for justice and to "expose
OL,11,Fthe truth" not only for himself but
OL,12,Ffor all his wronged colleagues.
OL,14,F"I didn't set out to spend 20 years
OL,15,Fdoing this. I hadn't expected to be
OL,16,Fdoing this so much by myself. It got
OL,17,Fmore and more complex," he told the
OL,18,Finquiry.
