OL,7,FAs Mr Bates gave evidence to the
OL,8,Finquiry, former Post Office boss Paula
OL,9,FVennells was today accused of
OL,10,Fmisleading the government after ITV
OL,11,FNews obtained a letter from March
OL,12,F2015, .
OL,14,FThis was despite the Post Office being
OL,15,Ftold in 2014 by the law firm it had
OL,16,Fitself hired to review prosecutions
OL,17,Fthat it found problems in at least 26
OL,18,Fcases.
