OL,7,FA Post Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fare deeply sorry for the hurt and
OL,9,Fsuffering caused to victims and their
OL,10,Floved ones and remain fully focused on
OL,11,Fgetting to the truth of what happened
OL,12,Fand supporting the statutory Public
OL,13,FInquiry, which commenced Phases 5 and
OL,14,F6 of evidence gathering today, to
OL,15,Fachieve this."
OL,17,FAs Mr Bates continued to give
OL,18,Fevidence, a petition demanding
OL,19,Fcompensation for people affected by
OL,20,Fthe Horizon IT scandal grew and has
OL,21,Fnow garnered almost 600,000 signatures.
