OL,3,CHorizon IT inquiry: Alan Bates says
OL,4,C'atrocious' Post Office is 'beyond
OL,5,Csaving'
OL,7,FFollowing the airing of ITV drama, the
OL,8,FPost Office has been under the
OL,9,Fspotlight for the scandal which saw
OL,10,Fmore than 700 sub-postmasters
OL,11,Fprosecuted and is now recognised as
OL,12,Fone of the biggest miscarriages of
OL,13,Fjustice in UK legal history.
OL,15,FThe sub-postmasters were handed
OL,16,Fcriminal convictions - with some
OL,17,Fjailed - between 1999 and 2015 after
OL,18,Fglitches in Fujitsu's Horizon system
OL,19,Fmade it appear as though money was
OL,20,Fmissing at sub-postmasters' branches,
OL,21,Fwhen in fact it was not.
