OL,7,FMr Bates and team flagged Horizon
OL,8,Fissues to Post Office helpline 85 times
OL,10,FMr Bates said he was initially "quite
OL,11,Fpositive" when the Horizon IT system
OL,12,Fwas introduced by the Post Office
OL,13,Fbelieving the new technology could be
OL,14,Fbeneficial to sub-postmasters' jobs.
OL,16,F"But I found it a bit frustrating once
OL,17,Fthe system was installed and we were
OL,18,Foperating, I found there were many
OL,19,Fshortcomings in the system," he told
OL,20,Fthe inquiry.
