OL,7,FIt was heard how he contacted the
OL,8,Fhelpline seven times on December 13,
OL,9,F2000.
OL,11,FOne of those calls was an hour in
OL,12,Flength. Mr Bates claimed the Post
OL,13,FOffice was "not really" of any
OL,14,Fassistance.
OL,16,F"The impression I got was that they
OL,17,F(Post Office) couldn't access the
OL,18,Fsystem any further than I could at
OL,19,Fthat time," he said.
