OL,7,FUp until Mr Bates was sacked in
OL,8,FNovember 2003, it was heard that he
OL,9,Fand his assistants made 507 calls to
OL,10,Fthe Post Office helpline, of which 85
OL,11,Frelated to Horizon and balancing
OL,12,Fproblems.
OL,14,FWhen Post Office CEO Nick Read was
OL,15,Fpressed by ITV News' Paul Brand about
OL,16,Fwhether his predecessors lied about
OL,17,Fwhat they knew about the Horizon IT
OL,18,Fissues, he replied: 'I'm not going to
OL,19,Fgo into the specifics of what my
OL,20,Fpredecessors did'
