OL,8,Fsacked because he became 'unmanageable'
OL,10,FThe inquiry heard Mr Bates received a
OL,11,Fletter terminating his employment as a
OL,12,Fsub-postmaster in 2003 with no reason
OL,13,Fgiven for his dismissal.
OL,15,FIt came after he refused to accept
OL,16,Fliability for shortfalls in the
OL,17,Faccounts at his branch in Llandudno,
OL,18,FNorth Wales.
