OL,7,FSlides were shown from an undated
OL,8,Fpresentation about Horizon integrity
OL,9,Fprepared by a former Post Office
OL,10,Fmanager, which claimed Mr Bates
OL,11,F"clearly struggled with accounting"
OL,12,Fbut said he'd become "unmanageable".
OL,14,FThe presentation, created by the
OL,15,Forganisation's former managing
OL,16,Fdirector of branch accounting Dave
OL,17,FSmith, read: "Bates had discrepancies
OL,18,Fbut was dismissed because he became
OL,19,Funmanageable. Clearly struggled with
OL,20,Faccounting, and despite copious
OL,21,Fsupport, did not follow instructions."
