OL,7,FMr Bates said he was unaware the
OL,8,Freason for his dismissal was being
OL,9,F"unmanageable", adding that he did not
OL,10,Fstruggle with accounting, and laughed
OL,11,Fwhen it was asked if he received
OL,12,F"copious support".
OL,14,FAn internal review of Mr Bates's
OL,15,Fdismissal concluded he was
OL,16,F"unsuitable" for the job and said:
OL,17,F"The decision to terminate was not
OL,18,Fonly right ` it was the only sensible
OL,19,Foption."
