OL,8,Fhim because "they didn't like me
OL,9,Fstanding up to them".
OL,11,F"Basically, I think it was because a)
OL,12,Fthey didn't like me standing up to
OL,13,Fthem in the first instance, b) they
OL,14,Fwere finding it awkward, and c) I
OL,15,Fdon't think they could answer these
OL,16,Fquestions and they had a feeling I was
OL,17,Fgoing to carry on in a similar vein
