OL,7,FMs Vennells, who led Post Office Ltd
OL,8,Fbetween 2012 and 2019, has come under
OL,9,Ffire over why hundreds of sub-
OL,10,Fpostmasters were wrongly prosecuted
OL,11,Ffor fraud and false accounting under
OL,12,Fher watch.
OL,14,FMs Vennells, who joined the Post
OL,15,FOffice in 2007, handed back her CBE
OL,16,Ffor services to the Post Office and to
OL,17,Fcharity, after the screening of ITV
OL,18,Fdrama Mr Bates vs The Post Office and
OL,19,Fensuing public anger.
